         My research is 160+ (163 maybe?) and if a budding necro comes to me with words and a book of dark combinings I click combine for free.  Hell its the least I can do to help out.  </P><P>I have been known to gather and combine the words for the 49 spells on my own and offer them up to necros in the 46-49 level range - for a nominal fee (generally 500p for the Pet49 if they don't want any others, or 400p apiece for two or more ... or 1500p for the set of all four.)  That is a little pricy but if I do all the work and just hand over all four research only spells at one whack most are eager to pay it.  I do it generally as a service and any of them that say 'no thanks' can still come to me with the words and I combine em for free.</P><P>Glonoin</P><P>Using your dead bodies to create a better tomorrow..<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
